# Assignment 6

## Change Network from NAT to Bridged and Compare Ping Results

### Aim

To observe differences between NAT and Bridged networking.

### NAT Mode

* VM receives private IP.
* Internet access through host machine.
* Hidden from local network.

### Bridged Mode

* VM receives IP from router.
* Appears as separate device on network.
* Direct communication with local network.

### Ping Comparison

| Feature        | NAT        | Bridged     |
| -------------- | ---------- | ----------- |
| IP Source      | VMware NAT | Router DHCP |
| Visible on LAN | No         | Yes         |
| Direct Access  | Limited    | Full        |

### Observation

Bridged networking provides direct LAN connectivity while NAT provides isolation.

### Result

Successfully changed network adapter and observed connectivity differences.

